name: What is This Thing Called Sleep?
description:
This poster was inspired by my experiences with lucid dreaming, sleep paralysis, and the concept of REM. The artwork features an original Rorschach design and a hidden strawberry stamp as my personal digital signature. 

Media: Conglomeration of xeroxed images from print media and original artwork collaged in photoshop

Dimensions: 4871 x 6200 pixels
